      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my pride and joy. I\u2019ve absolutely loved every mile in this beauty, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. She\u2019s in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, looking at her is like stepping back onto the showroom floor. I\u2019ve been meticulous with the upkeep, and while there might be a microscopic mark if you use a magnifying glass, she\u2019s about as close to perfect as you can get. This car drives like a dream and still has that wonderful 'new car' energy. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate how special this one is. Come on over, let\u2019s chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of her!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
